  "description": "The sequel to EA Sports' basketball title <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Lakers+versus+Celtics+and+the+NBA+Playoffs\">Lakers versus Celtics and the NBA Playoffs</a>.  The core gameplay of the original is supplemented with a variety of new features, including:<ul><li>All 16 1992 NBA Playoff teams  (up from 8 in Lakers vs. Celtics) plus the East and West All-Star Teams, plus courts with official team logos/colors. The rosters are based on the 1990/1991 season.<li> Player game stats updated while the game is in progress.<li>An Instant Replay mode.<li>New &quot;signature moves&quot; for star players.<li>Improved defense and passing controls and a foul shooting meter.</ul>Multiplayer options include cooperative and head-to-head modes.\n ",
